### Health Check

GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### Register User

POST http://localhost:3000/v1/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
"username": "harsh",
"email": "harsh@gmail.com",
"password": "password123"
}

###

### Login User

POST http://localhost:3000/v1/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "harsh@gmail.com",
"password": "password123"
}

