### Create Note

POST http://localhost:3000/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
"title": "My First Note",
"content": "Hello World"
}

###

### Get All Notes

GET http://localhost:3000/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Note By ID

GET http://localhost:3000/notes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update Note

PUT http://localhost:3000/notes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
"title": "Updated Note",
"content": "Updated Content"
}

###

### Delete Note

DELETE http://localhost:3000/notes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create Alarm

POST http://localhost:3000/alarms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
"note_id": 1,
"alarm_time": "2026-06-10T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Get All Alarms

GET http://localhost:3000/alarms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Alarm By ID

GET http://localhost:3000/alarms/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update Alarm

PUT http://localhost:3000/alarms/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
"alarm_time": "2026-06-15T12:00:00Z"
}

###

### Delete Alarm

DELETE http://localhost:3000/alarms/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Logout

POST http://localhost:3000/v1/logout/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
